{"type": "article", "id": 5769, "title": "“伐要搞，本来蛮好”，味全上海话广告叫板光明", "description": "高端鲜奶市场竞争也正在变得激烈，味全能够脱颖而出吗？", "date": "2015-02-02T14:25:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6680, "name": "味全"}, {"id": 6681, "name": "无调整牛奶"}], "category": 18, "column": null, "author": 1065, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155350XmyoxWqNDnf4pa6M.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">前有光明，后有明治，几条上海话病毒式广告能帮助味全在竞争激烈的低温鲜奶市场打开局面吗？<span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\"><p class=\"\"></p></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日前，味全为旗下高端奶品“无调整”鲜牛奶推出了以沪语为特色的系列广告。 无调整的概念源于</span><span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日本，酪</span><span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">农把早上挤出的生乳经过基本的杀菌灯工艺后就直接饮用。味全将“成分无调整”的行业术语，转化为广告语<span class=\"\">「</span>伐要搞，本来蛮好」，强化概念「牛奶最初的味道」。截止目前，＃伐要搞，本来蛮好＃新浪微博话题达到 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">2 </span>亿阅读量，评论过万。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061553499NRLvGrXTiCDPYIu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">选择地方方言作为广告语并不新鲜，此前光明牛奶也用上海话做广告，不过做为本土本品，这更容易理解，味全作为台湾顶新集团旗下品牌，此次也选用上海话拉近于消费者的关系，当然与上海市场强劲的低温奶消费能力相关。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;font-family:宋体;\">根据上海奶业行业协会统计，常温奶消费在全国的比例是 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">70</span>％，而上海市场和全国相反，低温鲜奶占据 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">70</span>％ 的市场份额。同时，</span><span class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;font-family:宋体;\">消费者对低温奶的需求在持续增加</span><span class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;font-family:宋体;\">，中国奶业协会数据显示，自 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">2013 </span>年起国内低温奶销售额年增长超过<span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\"> 30%</span>。目前味全“无调整”鲜牛奶主要集中在江浙沪销售。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;\">为了消除「伐要搞，本来蛮好」的文化</span><span class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;\">障碍，味全一口气推出了《老上海篇》、《春运篇》和《相亲篇》系列恶搞视频，集中微信资源进行病毒传播。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY1MDU4ODI0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">《老上海篇》</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t01445s5zt8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">《春运篇》</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY1MDczNzky\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;white-space:normal;line-height:19.5pt;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">《相亲篇》</span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;white-space:normal;line-height:19.5pt;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">随着三支病毒视频斩获 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">60 </span>多万频次点击，味全再次推出品牌视频广告，用上海阿姨“洗脑式”的「伐要搞，本来蛮好」将这句话深深打在味全牛奶身上，产生产品形象强关联。</span> \r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY2MzkxMjAw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;white-space:normal;line-height:19.5pt;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">事实上，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">下半年推出“无调整”鲜牛奶并不是味全真正意义上的全新产品，而是对 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2011 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年上市的“牛奶履历”鲜牛奶进行了一次重新包装和产品升级，同样升级的还有牛奶的价格。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155350L8FIH6rMD9GvBEzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">18.9 </span><span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元的定价，意味着味全正式进军低温鲜奶高端市场。而光明</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">作为最早进入中国高端低温鲜奶市场的先行者，凭借成熟冷链物流运输体系和品牌积累，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">AC </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">尼尔森数据显示，光明低温奶在华东地区市场占有率保持在 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">80% </span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">左右。尽管近年来巴氏低温奶市场竞争越来越激烈，涌现出大量新品牌如乔尼牧场、寿尔儿童牛奶、南阳牧场等，但因为缺乏准确有效的市场定位，仍然难成规模。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"\" style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在安全问题频出的现状之下，味全牛奶强推的“无调整”概念会使其脱颖而出吗？除了光明，同样拥有日本技术的明治低温鲜奶产品“醇壹”也是味全的直接竞争者，前者于 <span lang=\"EN-US\" class=\"\">2013 </span>年在苏州建立工厂，一举解决了物流成本以及新鲜度方面的硬伤。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}